someone spotted the reward giver in PoK.  With the information they gave it was both a charm that increases in stats as you accumulate flags and for every zone you have gained access too it gave an EXP award.  Not just AA exp but a raw EXP that went through however you had the split setup.<br>
<br>
This is were some people are speculating why it wont be live right away.  As someone who gimped a level 46 char through a few flag events could shoot up a bit in levels with the reward.  Also I noticed that the flags they recieved credit were ones that unlocked new zones.  Things like the POI factory key and lower CoD key didnt yield an award as they just unlocked portions of a zone that you already had access too.<br>
<br>
So far it looks better then a sharp stick to your eye.  Makes me wonder what type of cult took over SoE.  In the past few monthes they have brought us some nice changes to the game. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Hunter Cordar Silentwolf</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Forest Stalker of Tunare</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=34697" target="top">Cordar's Gear</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xlabikxbonekissah>Xlabikx Bonekissah</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.feebleminds-gifs.com/greenguy.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style='color:orange;'>Tavern Resident</span></span><br>  Posts: 848<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(6/11/03 8:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3298.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.cox.net/skoriksis/smilies/whap.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flag Reward revealed</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://necro.eqclasses.com/forum/topic.asp?TOPIC_ID=19078">necro.eqclasses.com/forum...C_ID=19078</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=585801"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/vicour1/XlablikxSig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
